# SwiftMove Packers & Movers — Landing Page

A responsive service landing page built for a Packers and Movers company.

## Features
- Responsive Navbar with smooth scroll
- Hero section with stats
- 6 Services section
- Why Us section
- How It Works (4-step process)
- Customer Testimonials
- Contact form with validation
- Footer with links

## Tech Used
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid, CSS Variables)
- Vanilla JavaScript